sOwGvcjy601vz3k5amYg.description: Hello, I am gathering a set of engineers capable of making a project for the hull of a yacht. Next step would be to make a 3D model in the (preferably) FEMAP software to calculate the hull strength and the stress that is present under the dynamic load.
